  <title>NRL: Canberra Raiders' Josh Hodgson wishes he had the RLPA in Super League</title>
  <content>
There's only one problem Canberra Raiders hooker Josh Hodgson has with the Rugby League Players Association - he didn't have them to call on when he was playing in the English Super League.
Hodgson showed his support for the RLPA by wearing the union's cap at Wednesday's press conference.

